text: Mayu Kishi-Kawagoe is a female Japanese international table tennis player. She won a bronze medal at the 2001 World Table Tennis Championships in the women's doubles with Akiko Takeda. ==See also== * List of table tennis players ==References== Category:Japanese female table tennis players Category:Living people Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
